        <h3>How do I scan a VIN?</h3>
        <p>Tap the "Scan VIN" button and point your camera at the VIN number on your vehicle.</p>
        
        <h3>Where can I find my VIN?</h3>
        <p>Your VIN can be found in several locations:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Driver's side dashboard near windshield</li>
            <li>Driver's side door jamb</li>
            <li>Vehicle registration document</li>
            <li>Insurance card</li>
        </ul>
        
